{"tid":1954010,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"哭泣聲絕無意義  它不會扭轉收息的心意","createTime":"2020-04-01T13:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T04:40:04.000Z","uid":31320,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"547882b05e9a71005fe6bd3b849183e407eaf6c0","tid":1954010,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"匯控是失去股價一手屍<br />\n<br />\n彷彿聽別人故事<br />\n<br />\n今天我竟可低吸多一次<br />\n<br />\n又再讓這刺痛一再開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底收幾多分息打乞嚏<br />\n<br />\n舊事藏夢裏也不再有意思<br />\n<br />\n誰要你再說返家鄉的句子<br />\n<br />\n到底收幾多分息打乞嚏<br />\n<br />\n除淨完欠缺了派息都可以<br />\n<br />\n而這晚卻說我跟你不可再試<br />\n<br />\nAll～～～ in 完從來不易<br />\n<br />\n這個你我早己知　但到這夜方派貨<br />\n<br />\n入匯控何幼稚　若是要掉轉買多一次<br />\n<br />\n放棄原來更易　就算以後沽爆你<br />\n<br />\n仍笑說　不介意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0053500c5476fadae01a02541e84a86dc92bb6c","tid":1954010,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"就黎變香港電訊<br />\n百幾蚊買黎退休個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f230f0fd0f7f5e82b1776264f29587649719d62","tid":1954010,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce42081af80a2fb53aefc5d95adb9e2d305c